                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">Quadrato</td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="27" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> dam
                </td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="27" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> dam
                </td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="27" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> dam
                </td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="27" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> dam
                </td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">108 dam</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
          Chi pronuncia le seguenti frasi: un rettangolo o un quadrato?
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <span>• "Ho un lato che misura 21 m e il mio perimetro misura 98 m."</span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 has-checked:bg-pink-300">
                <input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="R" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
                <span class="font-bold">R</span>
              </label>
              <label class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 rounded cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 has-checked:bg-pink-300">
                <input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="Q" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
                <span class="font-bold">Q</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <span>• "Il mio perimetro misura 160 cm e un mio lato è lungo 40 cm."</span>
