              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">Triangolo equilatero</td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">b = 6 cm • h = 5,2 cm</td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="18" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> cm
                </td>
                <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 px-3 py-2 text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
                  <input type="text" data-correct-answer="15,6" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white"> cm²
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">RISOLVI I PROBLEMI</p>

      <!-- Esercizio 4 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(4) %>
          Davide ha costruito un aquilone.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-1 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-3">
            <p>Osserva l'immagine che lo raffigura e calcola quanti centimetri quadrati di carta ha utilizzato per costruirlo.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>Area =</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="750" class="w-20 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
              <span>cm²</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p140/p140_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2", alt: "Aquilone" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 5 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(5) %>
          Un mosaico rettangolare è stato realizzato con piastrelle di ceramica quadrate che hanno il perimetro di 160 cm. Osserva l'immagine che lo rappresenta e calcola il perimetro del mosaico.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-1 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>Perimetro mosaico =</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="880" class="w-20 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
              <span>cm</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p140/output-1715932804140_314_1001_278_144.png", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2", alt: "Mosaico" %>
